data.title: Mrs Henderson Presents (2005)
data.meta_description: 2007 #31 Dame Judi Dench starts a nude revue on BBC Two tonight at 10:30pm.
data.text:
Judi Dench is clearly having a whale of a time in this 1930s-set comedy about a 70-year-old widow who starts up a nude revue.

It begins as light comedy with a gently risque edge (rather in-keeping with its subject matter!), but things get a tad serious when the war hits. Luckily the film finds its lightness again in time for the ending, which is much more suited to the general tone.

All told itâ€™s simply a bit of fun, but its overall quality just about nudges it into a four.
